OL,5,CSTALKING THE STALKER...                
OL,7, If you've ever seen aCbird of preyGin  
OL,8, action, you'll know what I mean when I 
OL,9, say it's a blood-curdling, awesome     
OL,10, experience...                          
OL,12, Yet these majestic birds with eyes     
OL,13, sharper than razor blades are          
OL,14,Cthreatened with extinction in the UK.  
OL,16, According to theCRoyal Society for the 
OL,17,CProtection of BirdsG"the stalkers are  
OL,18, being stalked" and are being illegally 
OL,19, killed at an alarming rate.            
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````1/7``
OL,21,        Bby Bernadette Carroll          
OL,22,D]MG FOR THE LATEST GREEN NEWS p161     
