OL,5,CSTALKING THE STALKER...                
OL,7,CPoisoningGis the main cause of bird    
OL,8, of prey deaths in the UK, claims Chris 
OL,9, Harbard of the Royal Society for the   
OL,10, Protection of Birds.                   
OL,12, "32 buzzards were found poisoned and   
OL,13, rarer species including five red kites,
OL,14, five peregrines, two marsh harriers,   
OL,15, oneCgolden eagleGand one white tailed  
OL,16, eagle were also victims last year.     
OL,18, "These poisonings involved the        C
OL,19,Cdeliberate misuse of pesticides."      
