OL,5,CSTALKING THE STALKER...                
OL,7,CShooting,Gafter poisoning, is the next 
OL,8, biggest threat to birds of prey.       
OL,10, Chris Harbard from the Royal Society   
OL,11, for the Protection of Birds says: "Last
OL,12, year we noted 32 shooting incidents    
OL,13, involvingCthe deaths of 35 birds.      
OL,15, "It's tragic - the nation has lost 12  
OL,16, buzzards,Ceight peregrines,Gfive       
OL,17, sparrowhawks and single individuals of 
OL,18, scarce species like hen harrier, honey 
OL,19, buzzard, red kite and hobby."          
