OL,5,CSTALKING THE STALKER...                
OL,7,CNest destructionGhas increased         
OL,8, dramatically with 15 incidents in 1996 
OL,9, compared to five in 1995.              
OL,11, "One of the most worrying was the      
OL,12, removal of aCgolden eagle's nestGin    
OL,13, northern England," says Chris Harbard  
OL,14, of the Royal Society for the           
OL,15, Protection of Birds.                   
OL,17, "Five hen harriers, four peregrines,   
OL,18, two buzzards and a merlin also had     
OL,19, their nexts destroyed."                
