OL,5,CSTALKING THE STALKER...                
OL,7, The UK's wildlife has enough pressures 
OL,8, to face without the extra threat of    
OL,9,Cdeliberate extermination,Gsays Chris   
OL,10, Harbard of the Royal Society for the   
OL,11, Protection of Birds.                   
OL,13, "ThisCsenseless slaughterGof birds of  
OL,14, prey is crazy as it could wipe out many
OL,15, rare breeds.                           
OL,17, "In order to prevent extinction, the   
OL,18, Government has toCstrengthen the laws  
OL,19, currently in place."                   
